latestPosts.caption:
The last few weeks have felt unusual for me. I had no idea that during these six months, so much would transform within me and my surroundings. I have visited the most stunning locations yet continue to feel unhappy. I have loved and lost. I have met prople who felt like home and also met those who made me feel like an outsider. I have felt pain but I continued doing things to make me happy. I have laughed my heart out and so have I cried till my eyes dry out the next minute. 
I have felt weak but also I have overcome every obstacle life throws. I feel stronger than ever in this few months and I have learnt to “Just keep swimming”

I left the original audio on to recall the enjoyable moments
✌🏼🤍
